# For this project I used SQL to querey the superstore database for items sold and their prices.

#Use a SELECT statment to order the items by price.
#1 Select item_name,price
FROM superstore
Order by price;

#Show a statistic about item price.
#2Select avg(price)
From superstore;

#Show a statistic on price in the category Kitchen Supplies.
#3Select Avg(price),category
From superstore
Where category='Kitchen Supplies';

#Create your own question. What is the MAX average rating for items in category appliances. 
#4Select Max(average_rating),category
From superstore
Where category='Appliances';
